newsitem.title: USA: Iowa-S Minn fed cattle not tested - USDA.
newsitem.headline: Iowa-S Minn fed cattle not tested - USDA.

text.p: Slaughter steers and heifers were not tested on a live basis, compared with Monday's close, USDA said. Trade slow. Demand moderate. Seller interest light. Offerings light and current.
Steers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 no sales. Heifers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 no sales.
Carcass Basis (weight only) Compared Mondays close -
Slaughter steers and heifers not well tested with a firm undertone noted.

Steers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 1200-1300 lbs few 116.00-117.00. Holstein - (weight only) Select to mostly Choice 2-3 1250-1400 lbs 105.00-107.00. Holsteins - ( grade and weight) Choice 2-3 1250-1450 lbs ld 108.00 Select 2-3 1250-1450 lbs 102.00.
Heifers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 no sales.
